channel.title: Are you a Deviant?
channel.description:
Bscly are you a member of [b][u][url='https://browse.deviantart.com/?order=9']deviantART[/url][/u][/b], the world's greatest art site?? [b]If yes, then post a link to your DA profile page here and I'll update this first post and add you to the list![/b]
This will help you expand your audience and you'll also get to discover other people's creations. You can even make new friends and add others to your devWatch. :slight_smile:

item.title: Are you a Deviant?
item.dc:creator: amazingcomedy
item.description:
pendulum:

Meh, deviant art. A site for art that lacks the design for an art site. Most of the people who use it just want to feel special because they drew a picture, there are a select few users who are actually good at “art” but all good posts are beeing over ruled by shitty artwork and anime… it is better to have a great online portfolio than an account.

Well, consider DeviantArt like YouTube, there’s stuff that’s good, stuff that you might not like but may be considered good by others, and stuff that is just bad entirely.

Read full topic
